snippet.title: Amber Heard Reacts To Johnny Depp Attacking Her!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has broken her silence on what happened on the night her ex-husband, Johnny Depp, attacked her. Amber Heard is finally speaking out about what happened with Johnny Depp in 2016. She said that she was kicked and had an iPhone thrown at her face! During her testimony, she said that he then grabbed around her neck and she felt the need to defend herself.
